originContent: # Folda-Scan: Your Private AI Navigator & Q&A Engine for Codebases 🚀
translatedContent: # Folda-Scan：您的私有 AI 导航器与代码库问答引擎 🚀

originContent: [![许可证: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
translatedContent: [![许可证: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

originContent: [![GitHub Repo stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/oldjs/web-code-agent?style=social)](https://github.com/oldjs/web-code-agent/stargazers)
translatedContent: [![GitHub 仓库星标](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/oldjs/web-code-agent?style=social)](https://github.com/oldjs/web-code-agent/stargazers)

originContent: Unlock your codebase with AI, all locally, with your privacy intact.xs
translatedContent: 用 AI 解锁您的代码库，全部本地完成，隐私安全无虞。xs

originContent: **Lost in a code maze? Tired of tedious context prep for AI collaboration? Folda-Scan to the rescue!** 💡
translatedContent: **迷失在代码迷宫中？厌倦为 AI 协作准备繁琐的上下文？Folda-Scan 来帮您！** 💡

originContent: **Folda-Scan** is a revolutionary intelligent project Q&A tool that **runs entirely locally in your browser**. It transforms your codebase into a conversational partner using advanced semantic vectorization, making code comprehension and AI collaboration unprecedentedly simple and secure.
translatedContent: **Folda-Scan** 是一款革命性的智能项目问答工具，**完全在您的浏览器本地运行**。它利用先进的语义向量化技术，将您的代码库转变为一个可对话的伙伴，使代码理解与 AI 协作前所未有地简单且安全。

originContent: Folda-Scan (as part of the [WebFS-Toolkit](https://github.com/oldjs/web-code-agent)) is built with cutting-edge web technologies and AI algorithms to offer you a smooth, efficient, and secure local code interaction experience.
translatedContent: Folda-Scan（作为 [WebFS-Toolkit](https://github.com/oldjs/web-code-agent) 的一部分）基于尖端的网络技术和 AI 算法，旨在为您提供流畅、高效且安全的本地代码交互体验。

originContent: ### ✨ Key Highlights (Why Folda-Scan?)
translatedContent: ### ✨ 主要亮点（为何选择 Folda-Scan？）

originContent: - 🛡️ **Absolute Privacy, Local Execution**: All data processing happens locally in your browser; your code **never leaves** your machine.
translatedContent: - 🛡️ **绝对隐私，本地执行**：所有数据处理均在浏览器本地完成；您的代码**绝不离开**您的设备。

originContent: - 💬 **"Chat" with Code in Natural Language**: Ask questions about your codebase as if talking to a colleague and get precise answers.
translatedContent: - 💬 **用自然语言“聊天”代码**：像与同事交谈一样提问代码库，获得精准答案。

originContent: - 🧠 **Deep Semantic Understanding**: Goes beyond keywords to grasp the true intent and complex logic within your code.
translatedContent: - 🧠 **深度语义理解**：超越关键词，深入把握代码的真实意图和复杂逻辑。

originContent: - 🎯 **Pinpoint Information Instantly**: Quickly locate relevant code snippets and files, even with vague descriptions.
translatedContent: - 🎯 **瞬间定位信息**：即使描述模糊，也能快速找到相关代码片段和文件。

originContent: - 🤖 **LLM Collaboration Accelerator**: Generate context-aware Markdown with one click, perfectly "feeding" AI assistants (ChatGPT, Claude, etc.).
translatedContent: - 🤖 **大语言模型协作加速器**：一键生成上下文感知的 Markdown，完美“喂养”AI 助手（ChatGPT、Claude 等）。

originContent: - 💰 **Slash Token Costs**: Optimize LLM interactions, significantly reducing API call expenses and latency.
translatedContent: - 💰 **大幅降低令牌成本**：优化 LLM 交互，显著减少 API 调用费用和延迟。

originContent: - 🛠️ **Smart Config Generation**: Assists in creating project configuration files like `Dockerfile`.
translatedContent: - 🛠️ **智能配置生成**：辅助创建项目配置文件，如 `Dockerfile`。

originContent: - 🚀 **Instant Onboarding**: Clear guidance to kickstart your code exploration journey quickly.
translatedContent: - 🚀 **快速上手**：清晰指引，助您快速开启代码探索之旅。

originContent: ### 🚀 How It Works
translatedContent: ### 🚀 工作原理

originContent: Folda-Scan's magic comes from its innovative **semantic vectorization engine**:
translatedContent: Folda-Scan 的核心魔力来自其创新的**语义向量化引擎**：

originContent: 1.  **Local Scanning & Indexing**: Securely scans your selected local project, converting code into high-dimensional vectors via semantic analysis, building a knowledge index locally in your browser.
translatedContent: 1.  **本地扫描与索引**：安全扫描您选择的本地项目，通过语义分析将代码转换为高维向量，构建本地知识索引。

originContent: 2.  **Intelligent Natural Language Processing (NLP)**: Understands your natural language questions and converts them into vectors too.
translatedContent: 2.  **智能自然语言处理（NLP）**：理解您的自然语言问题，同样转换为向量。

originContent: 3.  **Precise Semantic Matching**: Efficiently matches question vectors with code content in the vector space to provide the most relevant answers.
translatedContent: 3.  **精准语义匹配**：高效匹配问题向量与代码内容向量空间，提供最相关答案。

originContent: _All done efficiently in your browser, with your data privacy fully protected._
translatedContent: _所有操作均在浏览器高效完成，您的数据隐私得到充分保障。_

originContent: ### 🛠️ Tech Unveiled (Tech Stack)
translatedContent: ### 🛠️ 技术揭秘（技术栈）

originContent: - **Core Framework:** [Next.js 14](https://nextjs.org/)
translatedContent: - **核心框架：** [Next.js 14](https://nextjs.org/)

originContent: - **Local File Interaction:** [File System Access API](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_System_Access_API)
translatedContent: - **本地文件交互：** [文件系统访问 API](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_System_Access_API)

originContent: - **AI & NLP:** Advanced Semantic Vector Analysis, Natural Language Processing Algorithms
translatedContent: - **AI 与 NLP：** 高级语义向量分析，自然语言处理算法

originContent: - **Main Language:** [JavaScript/TypeScript - please specify]
translatedContent: - **主要语言：** [JavaScript/TypeScript - 请指定]

originContent: ### 🏁 Getting Started
translatedContent: ### 🏁 快速开始

originContent: #### Prerequisites
translatedContent: #### 前提条件

originContent: - Node.js (Recommended v16+ or v18+, refer to `package.json`)
translatedContent: - Node.js（推荐 v16+ 或 v18+，详见 `package.json`）

originContent: - npm (Version per `package.json`, e.g., npm@10.x.x) / yarn / pnpm
translatedContent: - npm（版本见 `package.json`，例如 npm@10.x.x）/ yarn / pnpm

originContent: - A modern browser supporting File System Access API (e.g., latest Chrome, Edge)
translatedContent: - 支持文件系统访问 API 的现代浏览器（如最新版 Chrome、Edge）

originContent: ### 💡 Basic Usage
translatedContent: ### 💡 基本用法

originContent: 1.  **Select Folder**: Authorize browser access to your local code project.
translatedContent: 1.  **选择文件夹**：授权浏览器访问您的本地代码项目。

originContent: 2.  **Wait for Indexing**: Folda-Scan will quickly build a semantic index locally.
translatedContent: 2.  **等待索引构建**：Folda-Scan 会快速在本地建立语义索引。

originContent: 3.  **Start Asking**: Query your codebase in natural language and unveil its secrets!
translatedContent: 3.  **开始提问**：用自然语言查询您的代码库，揭开其秘密！
